{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_87","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented FW-M6-003 end-to-end.\n\nThe operator bundle now has a dedicated coarse archive path in [geometry_contract.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/geometry_contract.py), and [surface_operators.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/surface_operators.py) now builds lumped-mass fine-to-coarse restriction, constant-on-patch prolongation, normalized transfer operators, patch mass terms, and a Galerkin coarse stiffness/operator derived from the fine surface operator. [mesh_pipeline.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/mesh_pipeline.py) now writes `<root_id>_coarse_operator.npz`, enriches `<root_id>_transfer_operators.npz` with physical and normalized transfers plus quality metrics, and records the coarse assembly rule and metrics in operator metadata. The contract docs were updated in [operator_bundle_design.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/operator_bundle_design.md) and [pipeline_notes.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/pipeline_notes.md).\n\nRegression coverage was extended in [test_multiresolution_operators.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_multiresolution_operators.py), [test_mesh_pipeline_build.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_mesh_pipeline_build.py), [test_config_paths.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_config_paths.py), and [test_geometry_contract.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_geometry_contract.py). Verified with `make test` (37 tests passed) and `.venv/bin/python -m